profile:
Keeping things simple I specialize in small repairs including drywall and painting. So feel comfortable calling me for the smaller jobs and save money. Only $15hr with just a 1hr. minimum. No travel charges and free material pick up (even while doing the job). 
Available evenings and weekends till 10pm + weekdays.
Painting – Wall Repair – Trim Painting
Taps and Faucets – Towel and Grab Bars – Doors – Hinges Shelves – Picture Hanging – Stair Railings
Cabinet Doors and Drawers – Smoke Alarms
Furniture Assembly and Repair – Drapery Rods and Rails
Switches and Sockets – Light Fixtures
Toilet Repair – Bath and Kitchen Fans
Plugged or Drippy Drains and Traps
Vent Fan/Cover replace or clean
Tub and Shower Caulking
